title: Cooler Thermoswitch
description: Get your electric fan to switch on at a lower temp
author: Loyale 2.7 Turbo
content: Get your electric fan to switch on at a lower temp, with a Hyundai thermoswitch. Hyundai #25360-24000, 90-96 Elantra (Loyale 2.7 Turbo provides a list of other part numbers that will work)
